    "longDescription": "AI Mobile turns one existing Codex task into a manager-only CEO control room for Windows. The exact root objective remains immutable while separate standalone or host-native Codex, Claude Code, Antigravity, and optional Cursor worker sessions/jobs execute dependency-ready delivery cycles. The official Codex CLI is used automatically only with verified ChatGPT-plan authentication and shares the measured manager reserve. Continuous-management cycles can be verified, failed, and extended under one run id, but cannot complete the root Codex Goal; only finite objectives can return completion permission. The plugin discovers models, efforts, quota windows, cooldowns, private routing preferences, and recent outcomes; packages transcript-free project context; coordinates bounded parallel workers; executes structured verification independently from model claims; and continues CLI work through a zero-model-token supervisor. Transition-aware status emits a seven-field CEO brief with root objective, owners, elapsed time, capacity, cycle progress, blockers, and the next intervention.",
